; Coverage for amount.cc
; Incorrect use of thousand-mark period when a comma was retroactively
; identified as a decimal separator (European style with wrong grouping).
; Input "1.12,345" scanned right-to-left: 3 digits then comma (tentative
; thousands separator), then 2 digits then period -- the period triggers
; retroactive decimal-comma detection, but offset (2) is not divisible by 3.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    1.12,345 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 9:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Food    1.12,345 EUR
                   ^^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: Incorrect use of thousand-mark period
end test
